  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Congratulations, you have been selected as one of our special cockroach exterminators! You have passed the rigorous screening process and have been selected as a Distinguished Cockroach Exterminator! This is a great title given to only a few percent of the world's best and brightest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cockroach Clicker is a game in which you crush cockroaches in various ways to feel good. To crush them more efficiently and pleasantly, you can purchase effects and items with the money you earn from cockroaches!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3485730/extras/a14b2770a89e80fed584bc82eb2a28dc.poster.avif?t=1750698463\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3485730/extras/a14b2770a89e80fed584bc82eb2a28dc.webm?t=1750698463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3485730/extras/a14b2770a89e80fed584bc82eb2a28dc.mp4?t=1750698463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are lucky, you may find a golden cockroach or a diamond cockroach with a probability of 1 in 100 million. Smash as many cockroaches as you want and become a wealthy man with a high income!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Congratulations, you have been selected as one of our special cockroach exterminators! You have passed the rigorous screening process and have been selected as a Distinguished Cockroach Exterminator! This is a great title given to only a few percent of the world's best and brightest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cockroach Clicker is a game in which you crush cockroaches in various ways to feel good. To crush them more efficiently and pleasantly, you can purchase effects and items with the money you earn from cockroaches!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3485730/extras/a14b2770a89e80fed584bc82eb2a28dc.poster.avif?t=1750698463\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3485730/extras/a14b2770a89e80fed584bc82eb2a28dc.webm?t=1750698463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3485730/extras/a14b2770a89e80fed584bc82eb2a28dc.mp4?t=1750698463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are lucky, you may find a golden cockroach or a diamond cockroach with a probability of 1 in 100 million. Smash as many cockroaches as you want and become a wealthy man with a high income!</p>",
